codex
I found one more robustness gap before finishing: if the seedable pool token is only liquid against a stablecoin pair, the current fallback would still miss it when the verifier is funded only in ETH. I’m adding a two-hop router fallback `WETH -> base -> token` while keeping the WETH flashswap as the preferred path.
apply patch
